                    <ab>+ In nomine Domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi Dei aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/305">Landolfus</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/154">Atenolfus</persName> divina ordinante
                        providentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">principes</rs>. Cum
                        principalis excellentia petitione dilecti sui iuste petenti clementer favet,
                        igitur noverit <rs key="#Assembly">omnium fidelium nostrorum presentium</rs> scilicet ac futurorum
                        sagacitas quia, sicut omnibus notum est, habuit bonae memoriae <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/194">genitor noster</persName> emptam a
                        partae <rs key="#Monasteries">aecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85" key="#Curtes #Monasteries">Sancte
                            Sophiae</orgName>, quae constructa esse videtur infra <placeName
                            ref="#places/110" key="#Cities #Monasteries">Beneventanam</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> unam <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> quae
                        vocatur <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/296">Ferrumanum</geogName>, in
                            finibus <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/605">Liburiae</placeName>,
                        pertinentem ipsius ecclesiae. Postea vero, recordantes non ne forte in eadem
                        emptionem aliquid offendisset idem genitor noster contra partem ipsius
                        ecclesiae, unde illius anima periculum in futuro saeculo sustineret, tunc
                        pro redemptione animae eius <rs key="#Commutatio">dedimus in cambium</rs> in
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> ecclesiae <orgName
                                ref="#juridical_persons/84" key="#Monasteries #Curtes #Agricultural_workers #Aldius #Fundi #Gualdi #Chestnuts">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> situm in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/109" key="#Castle #Monasteries">Casino</placeName>,
                        ubi nunc <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/332">Iohannes</persName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abba</rs> regimen tenere videtur, unam <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> nostram de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Agricultural_workers #Aldius #Fundi #Gualdi #Chestnuts #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Purchase #Inheritance #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            ref="#estates/295">Petra Mellaria</geogName>, que quondam fuit de
                            <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Inflow #Inheritance #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                                ><name ref="Gaido">Gaidone</name></persName>, et tulimus ab eodem
                        monasterio <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> ipsius ecclesiae
                        pertinentes infra fines de Benevento, loco ubi nominatur <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/606">Pantanum</placeName>, et
                        offeruimus illas in iam dicta aecclesia Sanctae Sophiae pro anima eiusdem
                        nostri genitoris. Modo vero iterum pro amore Dei offeruimus in eodem
                        monasterio Sancti Benedicti hos <rs key="#Aldius #Agricultural_workers"
                            >aldiones</rs> nostros commanentes in iam dicto loco <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fundi #Gualdi #Chestnuts #Agricultural_workers #Aldius #Royal_slave #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Purchase #Inheritance #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            ref="#places/604">Petra Mellaria,</placeName> pertinentes de eadem curte
                        de Gaidone, id est <persName key="#Aldius #Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Guttemarus de Petra Mellaria">Guttemari</name></persName>
                        filium <persName><name ref="Iobinianus">Iobiniani</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Aldius #Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Gizzolus de Petra Mellaria">Gizzolum</name></persName> fratrem
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers #Aldius #Royal_slave"><name
                                ref="Piniulus de Petra Mellaria">Piniuli</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Aldius #Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Ursus de Petra Mellaria">Ursum</name></persName> filium
                                <persName><name ref="Anisso">Anissonis</name></persName> et alterum
                            <persName key="#Aldius #Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Ursus de Petra Mellaria">Ursum</name></persName> filium
                                <persName><name ref="Benedictus">Benedicti</name></persName>.
                        Piniolum non ibi offeruimus, quia habet uxorem <rs key="#Royal_slave"
                            >ancillam nostram</rs>. Simulque et offeruimus in eodem monasterio
                        integrum ipsum <rs key="#Gualdi">gualdum</rs> nostrum et <rs
                            key="#Chestnuts">castanetum</rs> in eodem loco Petra Mellaria et <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fundora</rs> et omnes pertinentias quas in finibus de Petra
                        Mellaria habemus sive <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Inheritance"
                            >per hereditationem</rs> nostri genitoris, sive <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Purchase"
                            >per emptionem</rs>. Predictos vero aldiones cum filiis ac filiabus suis
                        et omnibus rebus ac pertinentiis illorum ibi offeruimus. Ex quibus omnibus
                        predictis hos nostre munificentiae apices exarari iussimus, per quos omnino
                        sancimus et perpetualiter habendum nostris et futuris temporibus, <rs
                            key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">offeruimus</rs> eosdem aldiones
                        in fato monasterio et omnia ut super legitur habendi ac possidendi iure
                        quieto sine contrarietate heredum nostrorum. ut autem haec nostra offersio
                        ab omnibus observetur, manu propria scripsimus et ex anulo nostro iussimus
                        sigillari. Signum dominorum nostrorum Landolfi et Atenolfi gloriosorum
                        principium. LANDOLFUS ATENOLFUS. <persName key="#Other_clerics #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">scriba</rs> ex
                        iussione supradictarum potestatum scripsi. <date>Datum VII kalendas Maias,
                            anno vicesimo octavo principatus domni nostri Landolfi excellentissimi
                            principis et anno octavo decimo principatus domni nostri Atenolfi
                            gloriosi principis, indictione prima. Actum in <rs key="#Cities"
                                >civitate</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/173" key="#Cities #Assembly"
                        >Capuana</placeName></date>.</ab>
                </div>
